🧠 Task 6: Critical Thinking (For your `solution.md`)

Why are branching strategies important?

In a professional environment (or a high-level gaming team), 
you don't want everyone changing the "master plan" at once. Branching allows:
  Isolation: You can experiment with a new tool without breaking the working app.
  Collaboration: Multiple people can work on different tasks (Task A, Task B) simultaneously.
  Review: Code is checked by others before it goes "Live" (Production).

